  ('FAR', 'Shareholders'' Equity & Share-Based Payment',
   'An entity has 10,000 shares of 10% cumulative preference shares with P100 par (P1,000,000 total) and dividends in arrears for two years including the current year. If P500,000 in dividends is declared, the preference shareholders receive:',
   'P100,000', 'P200,000', 'P300,000', 'P500,000',
